===Allocations===
* '''{{bgcolortext|byeup|Top 8 Teams}}''' from Group A, qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india pro series|}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Pro_Series/2026#Grand_Finals|Grand Finals]]'''
* '''{{bgcolortext|up|Bottom 8 Teams}}''' from Group A, move to {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india pro series|}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Pro_Series/2026#Semi_Finals|Semi Finals]]'''
* '''{{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}}''' from Group B, qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india pro series|}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Pro_Series/2026#Semi_Finals|Semi Finals]]'''
* '''{{bgcolortext|stay|Bottom 8 Teams}}''' from Group B, move to {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india pro series|}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Pro_Series/2026#Survival_Stage|Survival Stage]]'''
* '''{{bgcolortext|stay|All 16 Teams}}''' from Group C, move to {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india pro series|}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Pro_Series/2026#Survival_Stage|Survival Stage]]'''
* '''{{bgcolortext|stay|Top 8 Teams}}''' from Group D, qualify for {{LeagueIconSmall/battlegrounds mobile india pro series|}} '''[[Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Pro_Series/2026#Survival_Stage|Survival Stage]]'''
* '''{{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 Teams}}''' from Group D, are '''Eliminated'''.

